From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vince.ceccarelli@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 15:08:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix(ui):=20register=20Tailwind=20v4=20theme=20t?=
 =?UTF-8?q?okens=20=E2=80=94=20restores=20all=20invisible=20UI?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Root cause of the blank-page render: design tokens lived only in :root, so
Tailwind v4 never generated bg-primary, bg-accent, text-muted-foreground,
border-border, bg-muted, text-success, etc. Every button, the dark footer,
the stats bar, badges, and the chat launcher rendered invisible. Fixed with
an @theme inline block mapping all tokens; verified the utilities now exist
in the compiled CSS.

Also:
- AWS-style header: Contact us utility link + prominent accent CTA, desktop
  nav moves to lg breakpoint (tablets get the clean menu), slimmer bar on
  mobile
- Chatbot: accent launcher with AWS-style pulsating ring (pauses when open,
  respects prefers-reduced-motion); panel width/height clamped for phones
- Footer: AWS-style column + social band; 9 primary social channels with
  real brand icons (react-icons), rendered only when a real profile URL is
  configured — GitHub live now, others appear the moment URLs are added
- Fluid responsive type scale across hero/H2s/ROI numbers for all widths
- metadataBase set (fixes OG resolution warning)

package-lock.json intentionally excluded: run 'npm install' after applying
to regenerate it with your local npm, then commit it.
---
